<L>Thanne seide the Erle Terry:</L>
<L>'For loue y prey the, sir Guy,</L>
<L N="4995">That thou to my Contree come with me,<MILESTONE UNIT="Caius MS. 107 page" N="127"></L>
<L>As we sworne brethern bee.</L>
