<L>. . . . . </L>
<L>Amonges theim was moche blisse,</L>
<L N="6540">And there they soiourned, y-wis,</L>
<L>At their wille in solas:</L>
<L>Amys theim fonde all that nede was.</L>
</LG>
</DIV2>
